      "content": "Please do not make any changes to your medication without consulting your doctor first. Mixing sertraline with St. John's Wort can cause dangerous interactions, potentially leading to serotonin syndrome. You should discuss your side effects with your prescribing physician to find a safer adjustment to your treatment plan.",
